---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import PageBack from '../../components/PageBack.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="AI Workflow - 蜗牛之家">
  <PageBack />
  <section class="section-header">
    <p class="eyebrow">AI Workflow</p>
    <h1>AI Workflow</h1>
    <p>这里分成两类：Custom Skills 是你整理出的自定义工作流，Superpowers 是通用研发方法论和配套提示词。</p>
  </section>

  <div class="article-grid">
    <a class="article-card" href="/skills/custom/">
      <span>Custom</span>
      <strong>Custom Skills</strong>
      <p>architect、code-review、dev-workflow、story-craftsman 等自定义工作流。</p>
    </a>
    <a class="article-card" href="/skills/superpowers/">
      <span>Superpowers</span>
      <strong>Superpowers</strong>
      <p>brainstorming、TDD、systematic debugging、writing plans 等通用方法论。</p>
    </a>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
